---
// Small intro band above the studio. Tells the user what this thing does
// without a giant marketing block. Keep it tight: the studio itself is the
// hero of the page, not the copy.
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-16 pb-8 text-center">
  <p class="text-mint-glow text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em]">
    Wan 2.2 · image → video
  </p>
  <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-50">
    Make a still image move.
  </h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
    Drop a photo, write a short prompt, get a few seconds of video.
    Runs on a public Hugging Face Space, so it's free, queued, and surprisingly capable.
  </p>
</section>
